   ``These are notable people we're dealing with. We don't know
whether the attack relates to their business or personal lives.
There's a lot of different possibilities here,'' said police
spokesman Greg Armstrong.
   Aissa Wayne, 32, and mortgage financier Roger Luby, 52, were
attacked by two men Monday as the couple, who have been dating for
several months, returned to Luby's multimillion-dollar mansion
