suddenly George Bush tells you he's going to be the
environmentalist president?'' says one. ``And now suddenly George
Bush says he'll be the education president?'' says another.
   Ms. Voles said the new ads will be running while a set of four
ads dealing with ``the packaging of George'' continues. Those ads
depict Bush's consultants sitting around a table trying to
``package'' a candidate who has no positions that the American
people can support.
