changed America. Michael Dukakis fought us every step of the way.
It's not that they're not sympathetic. It's simply that they will
take America backwards. George Bush has the experience, and with
me, the future -- a future committed to our family, a future
committed to the freedom. Thank you, good night and God bless you.
